1
00:00:00,480 --> 00:00:03,480
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#f8fda6">POPURI</font></font></b></font>

2
00:00:01,770 --> 00:00:03,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As all of you are already aware,</font>

3
00:00:03,480 --> 00:00:07,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">this upcoming November 1st 
is Tani-kun's birthday!</font>

4
00:00:03,730 --> 00:00:07,990
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an8}<font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#314fc9">BOOM</font></font></b></font>

5
00:00:07,990 --> 00:00:09,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? It's Tani's birthday?</font>

6
00:00:09,860 --> 00:00:11,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was not aware.</font>

7
00:00:11,070 --> 00:00:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should I surprise him with? 
Oh, I just don't know!</font>

8
00:00:14,660 --> 00:00:16,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And don't stand around yakking here.</font>

9
00:00:16,500 --> 00:00:20,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Has Tani-kun acted like he wanted 
anything in particular lately?</font>

10
00:00:20,670 --> 00:00:21,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no clue.</font>

11
00:00:21,790 --> 00:00:23,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should ask him that stuff yourself.</font>

12
00:00:23,750 --> 00:00:26,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamada Man, have you 
ever gotten any surprises</font>

13
00:00:26,590 --> 00:00:29,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that made you happy 
or made a big impression?</font>

14
00:00:29,010 --> 00:00:33,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... Hm, I'm sure there were.</font>

15
00:00:33,760 --> 00:00:37,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What good is it asking Yamada? 
They're totally different!</i></font>

16
00:00:38,350 --> 00:00:39,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like an album or something?</font>

17
00:00:40,140 --> 00:00:42,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! How lovely!</font>

18
00:00:42,770 --> 00:00:44,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's got experience?</i></font>

19
00:00:44,520 --> 00:00:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But, you know...</font>

20
00:00:45,980 --> 00:00:48,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't know anything 
about Yamada's love life,</i></font>

21
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:50,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I feel a huge gap 
between us right now.</i></font>

22
00:00:50,650 --> 00:00:51,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taira, how about you?</font>

23
00:00:51,990 --> 00:00:52,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

24
00:00:52,910 --> 00:00:55,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about you? How about you? 
How about you?</font>

25
00:00:58,290 --> 00:01:04,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For that kind of thing... I don't think 
it's about the gift being right or wrong.</font>

26
00:01:04,210 --> 00:01:07,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's that someone 
remembered your birthday.</font>

27
00:01:07,590 --> 00:01:10,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Them wanting to celebrate 
makes you happy, right?</font>

28
00:01:11,970 --> 00:01:13,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not that I care, though.</font>

29
00:01:14,050 --> 00:01:18,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stare...</font>

30
00:01:21,810 --> 00:01:23,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so grown-up.</font>

31
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

32
00:01:26,860 --> 00:01:31,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I don't want him finding out 
so I can surprise him.</font>

33
00:01:31,820 --> 00:01:33,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're really set on that, huh?</font>

34
00:01:33,660 --> 00:01:36,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, it's his first birthday 
since we started dating!</font>

35
00:01:36,870 --> 00:01:41,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to make it so that Tani-kun 
can never go back to average birthdays...</font>

36
00:01:41,410 --> 00:01:43,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">by giving him something 
unforgettable.</font>

37
00:01:43,620 --> 00:01:44,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that a curse?</font>

38
00:01:44,420 --> 00:01:45,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's terrifying.</font>

39
00:01:58,430 --> 00:02:03,230
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial">YOU AND I ARE POLAR OPPOSITES</font></b></font>

40
00:03:18,220 --> 00:03:20,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happy Halloween!</font>

41
00:03:21,180 --> 00:03:23,350
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial"></font></b><font size="16"><font color="#80639d">(TANI'S BIRTHDAY EVE)</font></font></font>

42
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:22,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

43
00:03:23,350 --> 00:03:27,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun, you don't have cram school 
or library duty tomorrow, right?</font>

44
00:03:27,100 --> 00:03:27,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

45
00:03:28,190 --> 00:03:30,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then we have to walk together, okay?</font>

46
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:31,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

47
00:03:31,270 --> 00:03:33,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

48
00:03:33,110 --> 00:03:36,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's a walking-home-from-school 
birthday date!</i></font>

49
00:03:37,950 --> 00:03:39,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do I do?</i></font>

50
00:03:40,700 --> 00:03:43,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel like she's going to 
surprise me with something.</i></font>

51
00:03:45,200 --> 00:03:47,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In my class in middle school...</i></font>

52
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:50,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hinacchi! Happy birthday!</font>

53
00:03:50,790 --> 00:03:54,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Thank you, everyone! 
This makes me super happy!</font>

54
00:03:55,050 --> 00:03:58,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It was tradition for everyone to 
celebrate our classmates' birthdays,</i></font>

55
00:03:58,970 --> 00:04:02,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>because it'd be sad if someone's 
birthday didn't get celebrated.</i></font>

56
00:04:03,260 --> 00:04:07,520
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#ffffff"><font size="24">NOVEMBER
1ST</font></font></b></font>

57
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:06,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My turn came around, too, but...</i></font>

58
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:07,520
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24">TANI'S BIRTHDAY!</font></b></font>

59
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:09,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun! Happy birthday!</font>

60
00:04:09,810 --> 00:04:11,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happy birthday!</font>

61
00:04:11,270 --> 00:04:13,520
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24"><font color="#83f5c3">QUIET...</font></font></b></font>

62
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:12,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

63
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:17,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Your reaction's kinda underwhelming.</font>

64
00:04:18,030 --> 00:04:21,030
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial"><font size="16">*ACTUALLY GRATEFUL</font></font></b></font>

65
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:21,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I still don't know what 
the right response was.</i></font>

66
00:04:21,030 --> 00:04:21,970
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="18">reactions</font></font></b></font>

67
00:04:21,970 --> 00:04:23,340
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="18">reactions that make</font></font></b></font>

68
00:04:23,340 --> 00:04:23,380
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="18">reactions that make people</font></font></b></font>

69
00:04:23,380 --> 00:04:27,760
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="18">reactions that make people happy</font></font></b></font>

70
00:04:25,540 --> 00:04:27,760
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#8affd5">YAY</font></b></font>

71
00:04:26,660 --> 00:04:28,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is a problem.</i></font>

72
00:04:28,620 --> 00:04:31,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I doubt that I can act surprised.</i></font>

73
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:35,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taira, your reactions are so funny. 
It makes all the goofing around worth it.</font>

74
00:04:38,050 --> 00:04:39,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There!</font>

75
00:04:39,630 --> 00:04:41,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And better luck next time!</font>

76
00:04:40,550 --> 00:04:41,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right!</font>

77
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! Can it get any worse?</font>

78
00:04:45,390 --> 00:04:47,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh, I'm exhausted.</font>

79
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taira-kun, there's something 
I'd like to ask you.</font>

80
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:52,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

81
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:54,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are reactions something you work hard at?</font>

82
00:04:54,860 --> 00:04:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just what do you think I am, exactly?</font>

83
00:04:57,360 --> 00:04:59,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani! We're up!</font>

84
00:05:02,610 --> 00:05:06,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Was that about Suzuki's surprise?</font>

85
00:05:24,970 --> 00:05:26,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rain.</font>

86
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,970
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24">TAIRA'S
BIRTHDAY!</font></b></font>

87
00:05:29,220 --> 00:05:32,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Whether it's raining or sunny, 
it doesn't make a difference.</i></font>

88
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:35,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No one knows it's my birthday anyway.</i></font>

89
00:05:39,070 --> 00:05:45,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Happy birthday to you! 
Happy birthday to you!</font>

90
00:05:41,900 --> 00:05:44,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ayumi-chan! Happy birthday!</font>

91
00:05:44,990 --> 00:05:47,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? You did all this 
after school just for me?</font>

92
00:05:45,490 --> 00:05:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Happy birthday, dear Ayumi...</font>

93
00:05:47,410 --> 00:05:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no! I'm so embarrassed!</font>

94
00:05:50,700 --> 00:05:54,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Happy birthday to you!</font>

95
00:05:54,630 --> 00:05:56,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's mortifying!</i></font>

96
00:05:56,670 --> 00:06:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>For a second, I thought those guys 
had set up a surprise for me!</i></font>

97
00:06:01,590 --> 00:06:02,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taira.</font>

98
00:06:03,380 --> 00:06:04,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your face looks kinda red.</font>

99
00:06:06,390 --> 00:06:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it? Did you catch a cold?</font>

100
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:11,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. It's nothing.</font>

101
00:06:11,270 --> 00:06:13,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah? That's fine, then.</font>

102
00:06:15,350 --> 00:06:17,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taira, where's your umbrella?</font>

103
00:06:17,020 --> 00:06:21,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have one, but it's not raining 
hard enough to be worth opening.</font>

104
00:06:21,110 --> 00:06:23,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that just how guys work?</font>

105
00:06:24,110 --> 00:06:25,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was thunder.</font>

106
00:06:27,370 --> 00:06:29,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's hurry up and get back inside.</font>

107
00:06:34,250 --> 00:06:36,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is all this? Seriously!</font>

108
00:06:37,920 --> 00:06:40,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How unlucky can I get today?</font>

109
00:06:40,710 --> 00:06:43,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And on your birthday, too, huh, Taira?</font>

110
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:46,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You knew?</font>

111
00:06:46,470 --> 00:06:49,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We asked each other
that in English class, right?</font>

112
00:06:49,510 --> 00:06:50,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just remembered.</font>

113
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We did?</font>

114
00:06:51,970 --> 00:06:56,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You pronunciation of "October 10th"  
was way better than it needed to be.</font>

115
00:06:56,100 --> 00:06:57,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That last part was unnecessary.</font>

116
00:06:57,770 --> 00:07:01,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you hoping 
for an announcement at lunch?</font>

117
00:07:01,690 --> 00:07:03,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course not!</font>

118
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:05,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was joking!</font>

119
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:07,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right! I'll give you a present.</font>

120
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:10,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sticker that came with 
 the bread I ate at lunch.</font>

121
00:07:11,450 --> 00:07:13,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What's with the 
"I don't want it" face?</font>

122
00:07:13,950 --> 00:07:17,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just... my hands are dirty, 
so I'll accept it from you later.</font>

123
00:07:18,580 --> 00:07:19,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

124
00:07:23,550 --> 00:07:25,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! A yeti sticker!</font>

125
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:29,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's pretty cute. 
I wouldn't expect that from you.</font>

126
00:07:29,470 --> 00:07:30,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

127
00:07:29,890 --> 00:07:31,350
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#f36c24">YOU...</font></b></font>

128
00:07:34,350 --> 00:07:37,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Is that the one I gave you?</font>

129
00:07:37,690 --> 00:07:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taira, you're so conscientious!</font>

130
00:07:51,910 --> 00:07:55,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Should I stay up until midnight?</i></font>

131
00:07:54,830 --> 00:07:57,750
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial"><font size="20"></font></font></b>TANI'S NIGHTS
END EARLY</font>

132
00:07:56,660 --> 00:08:01,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If she does try to contact me, I don't 
want it to seem like I ignored her.</i></font>

133
00:08:04,130 --> 00:08:08,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No. Maybe I'm just being 
too self-conscious again.</i></font>

134
00:08:22,230 --> 00:08:25,570
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#ffffff"><font face="Arial"><font size="12"></font></font></font></b>INCOMING CALL</font>

135
00:08:22,230 --> 00:08:25,570
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#ffffff"><font face="Arial"><font size="12"></font></font></font></b>SUZUKI MIYU</font>

136
00:08:27,190 --> 00:08:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello?</font>

137
00:08:28,450 --> 00:08:31,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, great! You're still awake!</i></font>

138
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:33,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or did my call wake you up?</font>

139
00:08:33,740 --> 00:08:34,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was awake.</i></font>

140
00:08:34,790 --> 00:08:37,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, with that voice, 
you must've been sleeping.</font>

141
00:08:37,290 --> 00:08:41,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry! I'll hang up right after I say this,
so wait just a sec, okay?</font>

142
00:08:45,210 --> 00:08:48,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun, happy birthday.</font>

143
00:08:48,630 --> 00:08:53,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Um, I actually wanted to give you 
a more elaborate surprise,</i></font>

144
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:58,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but the simple truth is that I wanted to 
be the first to wish you happy birthday.</i></font>

145
00:09:00,520 --> 00:09:01,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Thank you.</i></font>

146
00:09:03,860 --> 00:09:05,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you were asleep. Sorry.</font>

147
00:09:05,770 --> 00:09:06,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wasn't asleep.</i></font>

148
00:09:06,860 --> 00:09:08,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's definitely a lie.</font>

149
00:09:08,740 --> 00:09:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It isn't.</i></font>

150
00:09:10,990 --> 00:09:12,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He sounds so sleepy.</i></font>

151
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:16,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, good night! See you tomorrow.</font>

152
00:09:22,540 --> 00:09:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love you!</font>

153
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:26,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just kidding!</i></font>

154
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:28,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah.</i></font>

155
00:09:29,550 --> 00:09:30,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Love you.</font>

156
00:09:34,890 --> 00:09:38,890
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#064385">ASLEEP</font></b></font>

157
00:09:35,010 --> 00:09:38,680
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#c6ffa6">ZZZ...</font></b></font>

158
00:09:43,810 --> 00:09:45,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning, Tani-kun!</font>

159
00:09:45,650 --> 00:09:48,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happy birthday!</font>

160
00:09:46,690 --> 00:09:47,860
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><i><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#e5087a"><font size="16">{\an8}WOO-HOO</font></font></font></i></b></font>

161
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Tani-kun, today's your birthday?</font>

162
00:09:51,650 --> 00:09:52,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happy birthday.</font>

163
00:09:52,740 --> 00:09:54,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Felicitations! Do you want a sticker?</font>

164
00:09:54,950 --> 00:09:56,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

165
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani, here. Gummies.</font>

166
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:59,700
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#0b72d3">BAM</font></b></font>

167
00:09:58,950 --> 00:10:01,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gummies. Thank you.</font>

168
00:10:02,580 --> 00:10:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani.</font>

169
00:10:07,340 --> 00:10:09,210
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font size="18"><font color="#e6e659">THUNDER
CHOCOLATE</font></font></font></b></font>

170
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:11,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

171
00:10:11,380 --> 00:10:13,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I have to get to work.</font>

172
00:10:13,130 --> 00:10:16,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's hiding the fact that 
he's embarrassed. That's so Taira!</font>

173
00:10:16,350 --> 00:10:18,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani, word is that it's your birthday.</font>

174
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:20,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My, how old are you now?</font>

175
00:10:20,810 --> 00:10:22,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The same age as us!</font>

176
00:10:22,230 --> 00:10:24,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that reminds me...</font>

177
00:10:25,100 --> 00:10:27,110
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#f7ea77">POPURI</font></font></b></font>

178
00:10:28,570 --> 00:10:30,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! It's on-shift Taira!</font>

179
00:10:32,740 --> 00:10:34,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's you guys.</font>

180
00:10:34,110 --> 00:10:36,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't go out of your way 
to come here on your birthday!</font>

181
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:41,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The birthday-ing 
is far from over, you know?</font>

182
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're buying stuff, too?</font>

183
00:10:51,050 --> 00:10:52,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

184
00:10:53,130 --> 00:10:54,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Belated good wishes.</font>

185
00:10:55,470 --> 00:10:56,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

186
00:10:56,340 --> 00:10:59,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taira-kun, I didn't know 
your birthday had already passed.</font>

187
00:10:59,970 --> 00:11:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not right if I'm the only one 
who gets a present.</font>

188
00:11:02,430 --> 00:11:03,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

189
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:05,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We heard from Azu earlier!</font>

190
00:11:05,770 --> 00:11:08,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly, Taira. Why the cold shoulder?</font>

191
00:11:08,650 --> 00:11:10,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happy birthday!</font>

192
00:11:09,150 --> 00:11:10,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please take it.</font>

193
00:11:12,690 --> 00:11:16,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, shall we be off, Tani-kun? 
Off to today's main event?</font>

194
00:11:16,450 --> 00:11:17,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I'm just a warm-up act?</font>

195
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:19,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Happy birthday!</font>

196
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this?</font>

197
00:11:28,460 --> 00:11:31,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taira-kun, did something nice happen?</font>

198
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:33,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's nothing!</font>

199
00:11:39,220 --> 00:11:42,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ta-dah! A lighter and candles!</font>

200
00:11:42,810 --> 00:11:44,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're very prepared.</font>

201
00:11:47,810 --> 00:11:49,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoops!</font>

202
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:53,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This might be just a little too much.</font>

203
00:11:56,700 --> 00:11:59,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now... we light them!</font>

204
00:12:01,620 --> 00:12:02,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Somehow...</i></font>

205
00:12:06,660 --> 00:12:10,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun, I'm looking forward to knowing 
the seventeen-year-old you.</font>

206
00:12:11,250 --> 00:12:12,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

207
00:12:13,340 --> 00:12:15,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This actually makes me really happy.</i></font>

208
00:12:22,220 --> 00:12:25,220
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="16"><font color="#f577cb">SHREWDLY, HAS HER OWN PORTION</font></font></b></font>

209
00:12:25,930 --> 00:12:27,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so good!</font>

210
00:12:29,270 --> 00:12:31,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want to trade a bite?</font>

211
00:12:31,100 --> 00:12:31,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

212
00:12:41,660 --> 00:12:44,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun, here. Your birthday present.</font>

213
00:12:45,410 --> 00:12:46,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A scarf.</font>

214
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:49,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's still a little early, but...</font>

215
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:52,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If he can only wear it 
with his regular clothes,</i></font>

216
00:12:52,670 --> 00:12:54,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll have fewer chances to see it!</i></font>

217
00:12:55,170 --> 00:12:59,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you wore it, it would 
make me super, super happy!</font>

218
00:12:58,010 --> 00:13:00,260
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial"></font></b><font size="24"><font color="#a7315c">OVEREXCITED</font></font></font>

219
00:13:04,970 --> 00:13:06,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzuki-san.</font>

220
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:16,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait. Is this...</i></font>

