<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Trebuchet MS"><font color="#e30f94"><font size="24">THUD</font></font></font></b></font>

231
00:13:22,700 --> 00:13:23,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

232
00:13:24,830 --> 00:13:26,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This makes me really happy.</font>

233
00:13:38,760 --> 00:13:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

