235
00:13:50,140 --> 00:13:51,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But since you gave it to me...</font>

236
00:13:52,690 --> 00:13:56,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! This weekend, let's go somewhere you 
want to go and do something you want to do!</font>

