<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Should I just go ahead and tell her that?</i></font>

250
00:14:42,990 --> 00:14:43,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No.</i></font>

251
00:14:43,990 --> 00:14:45,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun, want to grab one with me?</font>

252
00:14:44,990 --> 00:14:47,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Then I'll put the perfect plan together 
and show you around!</font>

253
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have one more self-centered request.</font>

254
00:14:46,910 --> 00:14:48,490
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#a527e7">{\an8}CUTESY...</font></b></font>

255
00:14:48,990 --> 00:14:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Could it be that I... 
am entirely too passive?</i></font>

256
00:15:02,380 --> 00:15:03,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Natural...</font>

257
00:15:03,880 --> 00:15:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">History...</font>

258
00:15:05,050 --> 00:15:06,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Museum!</font>

259
00:15:07,050 --> 00:15:10,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This might be the first time since 
my elementary school field trip!</font>

260
00:15:10,010 --> 00:15:11,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun, do you come here a lot?</font>

261
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:14,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. I just remember liking it 
when I was little.</font>

262
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:16,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you seem the type!</font>

263
00:15:17,690 --> 00:15:19,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's part of it, but...</i></font>

264
00:15:20,570 --> 00:15:31,580
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="28"><font color="#ee2e8b">{\an7}MOVIE
<font size="16"><font color="#ee2e8b">TIME REQUIRED:
2 HOURS 30 MINUTES</font></font></font></font></b></font>

265
00:15:21,190 --> 00:15:23,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There isn't anything good 
playing right now.</i></font>

266
00:15:23,320 --> 00:15:31,580
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b>{\an9}<font color="#f5682d">ZOO
<font size="20">TIME REQUIRED:
2-3 HOURS</font></font></b></font>

267
00:15:24,110 --> 00:15:25,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We went there before, though.</i></font>

268
00:15:26,070 --> 00:15:31,580
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="28"><font color="#3b8bf4">{\an4}AQUARIUM
<font size="16">TIME REQUIRED:
1-2 HOURS</font></font></font></b></font>

269
00:15:26,950 --> 00:15:28,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That seems a little short.</i></font>

270
00:15:30,830 --> 00:15:37,210
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="28"><font color="#0db299">{\an6}MUSEUM
<font size="16">TIME REQUIRED:
3-4 HOURS</font></font></font></b></font>

271
00:15:33,450 --> 00:15:37,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After worrying and fretting, 
this is the answer he arrived at!</font>

272
