<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="24">A
WORLD
OF
TREASURES</font></b></font>

274
00:15:37,870 --> 00:15:40,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Want to see the special exhibit 
while we're here?</font>

275
00:15:40,090 --> 00:15:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, let's go! Let's go!</font>

276
00:15:41,500 --> 00:15:43,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems pretty popular, too!</font>

277
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:46,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

278
00:15:49,140 --> 00:15:52,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't see anything at all!</font>

279
00:15:54,770 --> 00:15:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

280
00:15:55,980 --> 00:15:57,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tani-kun, where are you?</font>

281
00:15:57,980 --> 00:15:59,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzuki-san. Over here.</font>

282
00:16:00,360 --> 00:16:01,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

283
00:16:04,230 --> 00:16:06,490
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial"></font></b><font size="24">{\an8}30
MINUTES
LATER</font></font>

284
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:15,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All we could see were 
the backs of people's heads.</font>

285
00:16:23,380 --> 00:16:24,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

286
00:16:24,170 --> 00:16:28,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Why? Tani-kun, you don't have 
anything to apologize for.</font>

287
00:16:30,180 --> 00:16:32,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We still haven't seen 
the permanent exhibits!</font>

288
00:16:32,510 --> 00:16:35,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on! Let's make the rounds!</font>

289
00:16:37,350 --> 00:16:39,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

290
00:16:40,900 --> 00:16:42,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's easy to see things 
over here, isn't it?</font>

291
00:16:42,940 --> 00:16:44,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The exhibition halls are really spacious.</font>

292
00:16:45,190 --> 00:16:47,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow.</font>

293
00:16:48,400 --> 00:16:50,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is Emil's butterfly here?</font>

294
