00:16:50,240 --> 00:16:51,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's not.</font>

296
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:54,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so cute!</font>

297
00:16:55,450 --> 00:16:57,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Its legs are adorable!</font>

298
00:16:59,290 --> 00:17:01,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa.</font>

299
00:17:02,670 --> 00:17:04,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

