<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

313
00:17:43,420 --> 00:17:45,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, you had no control over this.</font>

314
00:17:45,380 --> 00:17:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's another restaurant nearby, so...</font>

315
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:50,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? You really did a lot of research!</font>

316
