<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go somewhere else.</font>

323
00:18:03,270 --> 00:18:04,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

324
00:18:04,650 --> 00:18:06,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From the looks of it, 
it's over our budget.</font>

325
00:18:07,230 --> 00:18:10,240
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#4b432c">SU</font></b></font>

326
00:18:07,610 --> 00:18:09,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd love to go there when I grow up.</font>

327
00:18:10,780 --> 00:18:13,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Suitable foodstuffs found!</font>

328
00:18:16,700 --> 00:18:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It gets chilly once the sun
 goes down, doesn't it?</font>

329
00:18:21,080 --> 00:18:23,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can feel that in my bones!</font>

330
00:18:24,210 --> 00:18:29,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Somehow, I feel like none of 
my plans went right today.</i></font>

331
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:34,220
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="16">{\an7}<font color="#e6247a">I WANT TO GO OVER THERE!</font></font></b></font>

332
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:34,220
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="16"><font color="#e78d4d">OVER
THERE</font></font></b></font>

333
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:34,220
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="16">{\an4}<font color="#fdffa9">HMMM</font></font></b></font>

334
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:34,220
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font size="16"><font face="Trebuchet MS">TIME
SCHEDULE</font></font></b></font>

335
00:18:29,710 --> 00:18:32,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Actually, have I been depending 
on her too much?</i></font>

336
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:36,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzuki-san, are you tired 
from all that walking?</font>

337
00:18:36,510 --> 00:18:37,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm exhausted!</font>

338
00:18:38,100 --> 00:18:41,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But because I walked so much, 
this food is delicious!</font>

339
00:18:42,270 --> 00:18:45,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a shame that we couldn't go 
to the restaurant that you looked up,</font>

340
00:18:46,440 --> 00:18:49,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but, in its own way, 
this can't be beat. Right?</font>

341
00:18:50,280 --> 00:18:53,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're always doing 
the things I want to do,</font>

342
00:18:53,150 --> 00:18:57,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so today, I wanted to do 
something that you wanted to do.</font>

343
00:18:57,120 --> 00:19:00,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm the one who ended up 
having fun again today anyway.</font>

344
00:19:03,830 --> 00:19:04,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

345
00:19:05,460 --> 00:19:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">like it better when you're 
having fun, Suzuki-san.</font>

346
00:19:08,130 --> 00:19:08,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

347
00:19:10,090 --> 00:19:13,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where we go, what we do...</font>

348
00:19:13,970 --> 00:19:16,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More than those places or goals...</font>

349
00:19:17,890 --> 00:19:20,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it's the time I spend with you, 
Suzuki-san, that I enjoy.</font>

350
00:19:23,810 --> 00:19:24,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

351
00:19:25,020 --> 00:19:27,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I totally get that!</font>

352
00:19:27,100 --> 00:19:27,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

353
00:19:27,190 --> 00:19:28,940
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font color="#0eb5a0"><font size="28">WHAT?</font></font></b></font>

354
00:19:27,900 --> 00:19:29,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the same!</font>

355
00:19:30,900 --> 00:19:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I say stuff like, "I want to go there," 
or "I want to do this,"</font>

356
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:39,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it's all really "I want to go 
to XYZ with Tani-kun," you know?</font>

357
00:19:39,700 --> 00:19:41,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the same! Just the same!</font>

358
00:19:42,910 --> 00:19:45,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Um. Is it different?</font>

359
00:19:45,330 --> 00:19:46,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

360
00:19:47,580 --> 00:19:49,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the same, too.</font>

361
00:19:50,080 --> 00:19:53,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suzuki-san, thank you 
for everything you do.</font>

362
00:19:53,090 --> 00:19:56,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Where's this coming from?</font>

363
00:19:57,800 --> 00:20:00,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? That's what you were thinking?</font>

364
00:20:00,430 --> 00:20:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish I could have done a better job 
of showing you around.</font>

365
00:20:03,770 --> 00:20:05,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was all just fine, though!</font>

366
00:20:05,890 --> 00:20:08,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I appreciate that you feel that way.</font>

367
00:20:08,980 --> 00:20:15,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know... Today, I was all, 
"Let's continue Tani-kun's birthday bash!"</font>

368
00:20:15,150 --> 00:20:17,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I made it so you had to be 
considerate of my feelings instead.</font>

369
00:20:17,360 --> 00:20:20,490
<font face="Comic Sans MS" size="32" color="#000000"><b><font face="Arial"><font size="16"></font></font></b>"BASH"
MEANING
"HUGE
BIRTHDAY
PARTY"</font>

370
00:20:17,780 --> 00:20:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Birthday bash?</font>

371
00:20:20,490 --> 00:20:23,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I was the one 
spinning in circles for no reason.</font>

372
00:20:24,160 --> 00:20:27,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the museum was fun.</font>

373
00:20:27,210 --> 00:20:28,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?!</font>

374
00:20:28,290 --> 00:20:31,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to go to that nearby 
art museum sometime, too!</font>

375
00:20:31,460 --> 00:20:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Let's go.</font>

376
00:20:33,420 --> 00:20:36,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I want to see all the colorful paintings!</font>

377
00:20:33,420 --> 00:20:36,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have some interest 
in European art history.</font>

378
00:20:40,340 --> 00:20:44,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I may be slightly lacking in 
an intellectual spirit of inquiry.</font>

379
00:20:44,430 --> 00:20:48,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I just have 
no artistic sense at all, so...</font>

380
00:20:56,780 --> 00:20:58,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'll see you at school.</font>

381
00:21:05,450 --> 00:21:06,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

382
00:21:32,810 --> 00:21:33,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good night.</font>

383
00:21:56,130 --> 00:21:57,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good night!</font>

384
00:21:59,130 --> 00:22:01,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Squee!</font>

385
00:22:13,350 --> 00:22:14,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Squee!</font>

386
00:22:14,690 --> 00:22:16,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm home!</font>

387
00:22:16,400 --> 00:22:18,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My! You look like you had fun!</font>

